  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the Evera MRI™ study is to confirm safety and efficacy of the Evera MRI ICD
      (Implantable cardioverter-defibrillator) System in the clinical MRI (Magnetic Resonance
      Imaging) environment when subjects receive MRI scans without positioning restrictions (MRI
      scans may occur anywhere on the body).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
